LINK: https://www.namastesql.com/coding-problem/61-category-sales-part-1?question_type=0&level_id=82791DA7C5D439BA

==> My approach:
SELECT category    
     , SUM(amount) AS total_sales
FROM sales
WHERE DATEPART(WEEKDAY, order_date) BETWEEN 2 AND 6 
      AND (MONTH(order_date) = 2 AND YEAR(order_date) = 2022)
GROUP BY category;
